uid":200,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"不孝有三無後為大<br />\n想做孝子就生返個俾老母玩下咪唔會怕佢悶"},{"pid":"723944448c77cdbdfaeb80e769330044679a76b8","tid":562014,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"我成日覺得阿媽係屋企好悶<br />\n但佢話勁多嘢做 一啲都唔悶<br />\n做家務 睇報紙 煲劇等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb162f8103d75517b68d1529a1b4f8f238b37b7","tid":562014,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"有仔女就無朋友<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主阿媽獨女？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我老母都類似<br />\n不過總算有幾個妹同表妹叔嫂親近<br />\n有節目下"},{"pid":"58fe7b088c1973a53f2e366d11733300241e064b","tid":562014,"uid":170190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"我成日陪佢行街"},{"pid":"c9b80a6870151b36db0017aaeb0f91eeb8a32c87","tid":562014,"uid":41009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得我爸爸好孤獨<br />\n每日就係開工 收工就返屋企<br />\n睇新聞睇電視用ipad上下網鬥下地主<br />\n間唔中同阿媽去下大陸旅行揼骨<br />\n搭親飛機通常都係過黎日本探我<br />\n同朋友出街食飯飲茶可能2-3個月先一次<br />\n<br />\n反而阿媽會1星期3晚左右唔係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又返狗會又去跳舞 好多節目"},{"pid":"93ded89417c32c427d5e786bce508eefab48043e","tid":562014,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb162f8103d75517b68d1529a1b4f8f238b37b7","tid":562014,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"有仔女就無朋友<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主阿媽獨女？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我老母都類似<br />\n不過總算有幾個妹同表妹叔嫂親近<br />\n有節目下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"唔係啊，佢都有同佢家姐傾既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但朋友真係零"},{"pid":"4811dec025598c7bfa9a80ce009384b6d6cc846e","tid":562014,"uid":122622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實可以睇下社區中心 幫下呀媽報d班上下 就會無咁悶又可以識到班朋友"},{"pid":"eae39ae2176cd182c2c1aa8d58c17dc3195eed75","tid":562014,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"我個邊情況有點似<br />\n不過我父母好早離左婚<br />\n而家我同兩個家姐都唔同原因搬曬出去<br />\n我就因為番工太遠，頂唔順大西北，一日用三到四個鐘交通，所以搬左出市區住<br />\n<br />\n我覺得個case仲lonely過你個個<br />\n但有時生活真係無辦法，我能做就係盡力抽多點時間番去陪佢"},{"pid":"d4ec49acfa7ccab915b03f413029f8e207dbf48b","tid":562014,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老豆都係<br />\n屋企人又成日唔陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df00d9214cdb1e4932c197c127bdfdad49ab5fe","tid":562014,"uid":44118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7e40f812f9b7f931396829863337c9d15622993","tid":562014,"uid":88109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"其實我阿爸早死<br />\n我家姐又嫁左<br />\n我細佬又要出街<br />\n我有時候都2邊不是人，今日岩岩做完野，今朝✈️返黎都唔知陪媽咪定陪女朋友？<br />\n我想2個都陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"今日三個一齊食聽日再同女兩個食多次咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔係咪同女友一齊行下街先 再一齊去搵阿媽食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5400944ffd77c57df828945697665b5298b5726","tid":562014,"uid":9856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"老母可能係毒撚"},{"pid":"672d132fe358f483fcfeadeff60acf98a0a33300","tid":562014,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db56bbf6d94a007b07b7e69d156cd6aadc6fae0e","tid":562014,"uid":200,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"不孝有三無後為大<br />\n想做孝子就生返個俾老母玩下咪唔會怕佢悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"有錢就話<br />\n窮人生仔正仆街落地獄"},{"pid":"be50830bf7d68493fe988a88605a4f4a